main event: A photograph of a circular, disk-shaped unidentified aerial phenomenon was taken in Junauska, North Carolina on March 30, 1967.
interesting points: The photograph shows a round, disk-shaped object hovering over a landscape, possibly a field or open area.
There are no human figures visible in the image.
The report indicates that two photographs of the UFO were taken.
The report is from the Foreign Technology Division of the Air Force Systems Command (AFSC).
The document is marked as 'UNCLASSIFIED' on both pages.
